---
title: Pork & Mustard Thyme Sauce with Parmesan Mash & Veggies
description: Give meat and three veg an upgrade with an array of flavoursome sides. Seared pork gets a tangy wholegrain mustard and thyme sauce, and we’ve taken classic mashed potatoes to new heights by stirring through Parmesan cheese. This is a modern meal that satisfies that comfort food craving!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/pork-mustard-thyme-sauce-9c9b4800.jpg
